    "white), and are therefore masked.",
    "Mosaic mask constructionFinally, we constructed mosaic masks for science use and calculation of the fiducial survey area for KiDS.",
    "Mosaic masks are constructed using SWARP combining all individual ten-band masks using a 'minimum' combination.",
    "Masks are constructed on a predefined WCS, using an Aitoff projection and a 6 ′′ pixel resolution.A170, page 27 of 54 Wright, A. H., et al.",
    ": A&A, 686, A170 (2024) Using these mosaic masks, we are able to calculate the area of the KiDS DR5 data when selecting specific mask bits."
